IF you're a Kaizer Chiefs fan and a staunch Moja Love TV viewer, then you'd agree that the Rea Tsotella anchor, Pastor I Makamu and goalie Daniel Akpeyi have a serious resemblance. Could their striking resemblance be that they were somehow separated at birth? Bishop Makamu is a South African televangelist, founder and senior pastor of Endless Hope Bible Church, which has been in existence for over 10 years now. The 34-year-old Akpeyi, who took over the No.1 goalkeeper's gloves at Chiefs from Itumeleng Khune, was born in Nnewi, Nigeria. Do you agree that the duo look the same? Share with us more on who in the PSL or GladAfrica Championship do you think have a striking resemblance in the celebrity world.